Description:
   Jackal's Verdict is a high-level Cleric area-effect divine offensive
   spell. Named for the jackal — divine herald of death and transition in
   the Disk theology — the spell invokes the god's judgment against all
   enemies present, dealing holy damage to every hostile target in the room.

   The jackal aspect of Disk governs the transition between life and death,
   and this spell channels that transitory force as a weapon. It is the
   Cleric's signature high-level AoE divine blast, available at a later
   tier than Disk's Word and dealing a different flavor of divine damage.
   Jackal's Verdict is particularly devastating against undead and unholy
   creatures, who are especially vulnerable to the divine transitional energy
   the spell channels.
